{"tid":1856832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國從中國武漢撤僑軍機降落法蘭克福機場。","createTime":"2020-02-01T22:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T07:00:25.000Z","uid":125193,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1a8a638e544fadc64bde003b1d27dc1f197405d7","tid":1856832,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T22:45:48.000Z","msg":"德國新增一名新型冠狀病毒確診患者，累計8宗病例。<br />\n<br />\n巴伐利亞州衛生部說，新增的患者是一名33歲男子。報道說，德國8名確診患者中，7人來自巴伐利亞州一間企業，其餘一人是患者家屬。<br />\n<br />\n另外，德國派往武漢撤僑的軍機已於當地周六回國。<br />\n<br />\n機上有102名德國公民和26名外國人。由於俄羅斯拒絕讓飛機在莫斯科降落加油，飛機經過延誤後，降落法蘭克福機場。<br />\n<br />\n德國衛生部長說，機上乘客沒有人出現病徵，<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506141-20200202.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506141-20200202.htm&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXtxjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=db3252c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506141-20200202.htm&h=85d27039\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506141-20200202.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6f1f4c5ff2b7d417e82ee78e4084962ef42916c6","tid":1856832,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T22:50:59.000Z","msg":"傳媒有無軍機降落武漢嘅畫面？德國人喺武漢上機嘅畫面？"},{"pid":"f9d4bce83823e90f7491b49484b9c3e82fac91d9","tid":1856832,"uid":149844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T22:54:17.000Z","msg":"軍機 已經係常識<br />\n唔到你中共講話唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為你啲武漢人走到全世界都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb698b7fd46bfe3266f11e13dc51af2a1443b3cf","tid":1856832,"uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6f1f4c5ff2b7d417e82ee78e4084962ef42916c6","tid":1856832,"uid":66242,